Uses of Interface
org.opengis.referencing.crs.GeodeticCRS

  • Packages that use GeodeticCRS 
    Package Description
    org.opengis.referencing.crs
    Coordinate reference systems (coordinate systems with a datum).

    • Uses of GeodeticCRS in org.opengis.referencing.crs

      Subinterfaces of GeodeticCRS in org.opengis.referencing.crs 
      Modifier and Type Interface and Description
      interface  GeocentricCRS
      A 3D coordinate reference system with the origin at the approximate centre of mass of the earth.
      interface  GeographicCRS
      A coordinate reference system based on an ellipsoidal approximation of the geoid; this provides an accurate representation of the geometry of geographic features for a large portion of the earth's surface.
